WEBVTT

00:02.294 --> 00:04.160
There was a guard
who was getting suspicious

00:04.254 --> 00:05.540
of what was
going on in there.

00:05.631 --> 00:06.816
They wanted me
to put him down.

00:06.840 --> 00:08.502
I told him
I wouldn't do it

00:08.592 --> 00:10.752
until whoever was running
the show came to me directly.

00:10.844 --> 00:15.179
- And who exactly was that?
- Roger Shapiro. CEO of Reform Corp.

00:15.265 --> 00:17.222
- And then what happened?
- I killed him.

00:18.060 --> 00:19.801
So you two
are in on this together.

00:19.895 --> 00:21.511
I have no idea
what you're talking about.

00:21.605 --> 00:24.393
You're never gonna pull
this shit again on prisoners.

00:24.483 --> 00:26.691
That's a signed confession
from Roger Shapiro,

00:26.777 --> 00:28.129
saying he entered
into a conspiracy

00:28.153 --> 00:30.270
and that conspiracy
was arranged by you.

00:30.364 --> 00:32.151
Look, I'm not going
to stand here

00:32.241 --> 00:34.733
and write my resignation letter
in front of you two.

00:34.868 --> 00:37.055
- What's going on with you and Brian?
- Donna, he's married.

00:37.079 --> 00:38.115
I would never do it.

00:38.205 --> 00:40.391
I know, but I also know that
the heart doesn't always listen

00:40.415 --> 00:42.015
to what the brain
says it would never do.

00:42.084 --> 00:43.495
- Denise Gallo?
- Who are you?

00:43.585 --> 00:45.827
Someone who knew your father.
He wanted you to have this.

00:46.630 --> 00:47.710
- Did you know?
- Know what?

00:47.756 --> 00:50.151
That Gavin Andrews was gonna
ask me to launder money for him?

00:50.175 --> 00:52.007
I knew he was gonna
ask you to do something.

00:52.094 --> 00:53.210
Help me get out of this.

00:53.303 --> 00:54.572
What the hell did you do
with my money?

00:54.596 --> 00:55.990
I found you a legitimate
business opportunity.

00:56.014 --> 00:57.550
- You're fired.
- I don't think so.

00:57.641 --> 00:58.927
Because if I can
do this to you,

00:59.017 --> 01:00.679
imagine what I can
do for you.

